  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5358441/" class="title-link">日本在边境，我们呢？</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5358441"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36771726-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">唐山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-03-24"
      class="main-meta">2012-03-24 10:50:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5358441_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这是一本通俗的“论日本”著作，作者内田树试图用“边境”来概括日本国民性。  所谓边境，是指日本文明并非内生，而是先后向中国、西方学习后才形成的，这就造成了独特的国民性，比如不问对错，不加判断，先照单全收，放弃价值判断，只看实际效果。因为只有文明中心的人才考虑...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5358441/#comments">(27回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
